  <brief_title>Study on Metabolic Parameters of Sertindole in Patients With Schizophrenia</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Exploratory Study Conducted as an add-on to Clinical Trial 11286, to Evaluate the Metabolic Effect of up to 12 Weeks Treatment With Sertindole and Olanzapine in Patients With Schizophrenia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
